11 2. (1) This state shall not be liable on any notes or
12 bonds of any port authority.
13 (2) Any such notes or bonds shall not be a debt of the
14 state and shall contain on the faces thereof a statement to
15 such effect.
16 (3) The failure to include such statement on the faces
17 of such notes or bonds shall neither invalidate the notes or
18 bonds nor render the state liable on such notes or bonds.
19 3. No commissioner of any port authority or any
20 authorized person executing port authority notes or bonds
21 shall be liable personally on said notes or bonds or shall
22 be subject to any personal liability or accountability by
23 reason of the issuance thereof.
24 4. The notes and bonds of every port authority are
25 securities in which all public officers and bodies of this
26 state and all political subdivisions and municipalities, all
